query:
SELECT i.fromDeviceId, a.username, a.platform, a.status, i.status as interaction_status, i.errorMessage
FROM interactions i 
LEFT JOIN accounts a ON i.fromAccountId = a.id 
WHERE i.interactionType = 'like' 
ORDER BY i.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 3;
